{"tid":1086611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教宗暗批特朗普:終被圍牆自困","createTime":"2019-04-01T01:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T01:43:29.000Z","uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"163929463ff709b3c92c03b3ae8d7b1f97d9b230","tid":1086611,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:17:06.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普在南部邊境興建圍牆，又揚言如果墨西哥不阻止非法移民進入美國，他可能會關閉美墨邊境。教宗方濟各不點名批評特朗普的做法。<br />\n<br />\n教宗結束摩洛哥訪問，周日在回程的專機上對記者表示，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">用磚頭和鐵絲網建造圍牆、試圖阻止移民入境的的政治領袖，最終將被自己興建的圍牆所困。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n教宗沒有直接提到特朗普的名字，但他過往在移民問題上與特朗普意見不合，移民問題成為記者追問的重點。<br />\n<br />\n教宗表示，明白到移民問題是一個燙手山芋，但政客應該使用其他方法解決問題，而不是用磚頭和鐵絲網。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在2016年競選總統時提倡興建美墨邊境圍牆，以阻截非法入境者進入美國。他上任後，美國國會未有撥出足夠款項建牆，特朗普較早前宣布國家進入緊急狀態的方式，以調撥資金興建圍牆。"},{"pid":"2d87724a2065db15bfa672216ffbce786690ef2f","tid":1086611,"uid":4493,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:19:28.000Z","msg":"梵蒂岡圍牆呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gcDGDf7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgcDGDf7.png&h=893caacc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b4ed6dc82809114b5d64bfcdaa5ecd2b2f473b72","tid":1086611,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:19:53.000Z","msg":"那是非法移民 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9efa23794651ed4e377f681f1f28042054ae414","tid":1086611,"uid":236646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:22:00.000Z","msg":"教宗識鬼政治咩....."},{"pid":"f60d4f579d5b654e5b3377987fdac1d3f2ff356e","tid":1086611,"uid":75994,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:22:06.000Z","msg":"教宗條友係咪老到傻咗... ?"},{"pid":"3ba98fa3d05444ce6c59c7d8ce7fdbfcb0a974fa","tid":1086611,"uid":54472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:22:39.000Z","msg":"乜撚野係移民入境的政府領袖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eff033cff17c011eb4be270f3f0a40d15ac4f77","tid":1086611,"uid":54472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:22:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜撚野係移民入境的政治領袖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8a3030eda69f7f0e7b814f99c4c5131f3f77ae98","tid":1086611,"uid":37111,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:32:16.000Z","msg":"阻止<strong>非法</strong>移民有乜問題<br />\n<br />\nisis戰士難民係咪可以移民梵蒂岡,開放聖彼得大教堂收容佢哋?<br />\n<br />\n河南省新鄉燒十字架,温州拆教堂,廣州獎勵舉報「非法宗教」,<br />\n新疆穆斯林「再教育營」,西藏藏民「再教育營」<br />\n咁多違反宗教自由嘅嘢,反而同中共示好,簽協議背叛地下教會<br />\n幾時暗批習近平?"},{"pid":"c93a6058e6d7d56ff2132d163f7546119de1a2e6","tid":1086611,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:38:50.000Z","msg":"送哂去煩帝肛囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b307d6d7e81e83688b57e3c69a45bb67f3985072","tid":1086611,"uid":29880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:39:26.000Z","msg":"你同支那講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034395cc0965fad8ade399724fd00a30820331bb","tid":1086611,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:40:35.000Z","msg":"唔通奶支, 接受雜種版聖經會win? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b96277973f9df7f45b103e792a5319ea40935a9","tid":1086611,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:41:33.000Z","msg":"梵蒂岡發大財"},{"pid":"c3e4694876c2b27c47bcb07e005e447e24051252","tid":1086611,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:42:20.000Z","msg":"難怪有人預言佢係最後一個教宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37f4224486edf355e9a6f1c8118b884dfb0c6fe","tid":1086611,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b96277973f9df7f45b103e792a5319ea40935a9","